Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 Section I E.2 | Description :The Recipient shall: (a) not later than thirty days afterEffectiveness, open and maintain an escrow account in a commercial bank on terms and conditions satisfactory to the Association,including appropriate protection against set-off, seizure or attachment (“Escrow Account”); (b) thereafter, but not later thanDecember 31, 2011, deposit into the Escrow Account such amounts as shall be required | Due Date :31-Dec-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1, A.1. | Description :The Recipient shall ensure that TANROADS is maintained at all timesduring the implementation of the Project with functions, staffing and resources satisfactory to the Association. | Frequency :Yearly
